  "texts": [
    "[40], analyzed basic SIEM capabilities and deployed Wazuh in a test environment.",
    "Bernardo et al.",
    "[41] evaluated the attack detection capability of Wazuh in a test environment by simulating multiple attacks.",
    "However, other open-source SIEM solutions such as OSSIM and SIE-Monster were dropped due to insufficient documentation and lack of resources required to deploy the solution.",
    "Hence these studies did not provide a comparative analysis with other SIEM solutions."
  ]
